        "description": "Create a new customer for the authenticated company.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (COMPANY role)\n\n**Request Body:**\n- name (string, required): 2-150 characters\n- email (string, optional): Valid email format\n- telephone (string, optional): Max 20 characters\n- mobile (string, optional): Max 20 characters\n- address (object, optional): Nested address details\n  - houseNumber (string, optional): House or building number\n  - street (string, optional): Street name\n  - city (string, optional): City name\n  - county (string, optional): County or region\n  - postalCode (string, optional): UK postal code\n  - country (string, optional): Country name\n\n**Business Logic:**\n- Customer is associated with the company of the authenticated user\n- Name should be unique per company (enforced at service/repository level)\n\n**Response:** Created customer object with metadata (id, timestamps, archived flag)."
      },
